{"tid":874455,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"人蠢沒藥醫！老闆叫搶匪打烊再來　一來就被警察抓走","createTime":"2018-10-24T08:10:28.000Z","updateTime":"2018-10-24T08:47:12.000Z","uid":122,"like":12,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":6,"replies":[{"pid":"bcf7dac55d337398fd5be17ea1ca23d23d3f5717","tid":874455,"uid":122,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-10-24T08:10:28.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://img.appledaily.com.tw/images/ReNews/20181024/640_a34ad6fdadbd00cb459b4e0135f0c3f6.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.appledaily.com.tw%2Fimages%2FReNews%2F20181024%2F640_a34ad6fdadbd00cb459b4e0135f0c3f6.jpg&h=a6be3177&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n比利時出現一批「最聽話」的搶匪，因為老闆叫他們打烊後再來行搶，他們還真的照辦，但下場就是遭埋伏警方逮捕。<br />\n <br />\n比利時夏勒華（Charleroi）郊區一間電子菸販售商上周六突然在光天化日之下遇搶，6名搶匪走入店裡要老闆交出現金。但店老闆迪迪爾（Didier）非常機智，先是稱兄道弟和搶匪搏感情，再說服他們「晚點再來搶」。迪迪爾說：「我跟他們解釋，下午3點不是搶劫的好時候。只能搶走大約1千歐元，但如果晚一點再來，就可以搶比較多錢。」<br />\n <br />\n迪迪爾向搶匪說，若等到店打烊的時候再來，就可以給他們2、3千歐元。結果這群人還真的信以為真，雙手空空離開店裡，約好晚一點再來。<br />\n <br />\n迪迪爾騙走搶匪後立刻打電話報警，但警方研判搶匪不可能再出現，除非實在笨到家。沒想到，商店打烊前1小時、當天下午5時半，搶匪果然又出現，迪迪爾當時還對搶匪開玩笑說：「你們應該要去買支手錶，現在是5點半，不是6點半。」<br />\n <br />\n搶匪又聽話離開。一小時後，搶匪第3次來行搶時，在店外等待他們的是便衣警察，當下就逮捕5人，第6人則是逃之夭夭。（桂家齊／綜合外電報導）"},{"pid":"847fde5b7bb5d9adea659a5d4a1da59cf35e621b","tid":874455,"uid":147264,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-10-24T08:13:13.000Z","msg":"第6個人走得甩<br />\n分分鐘搵個老闆報仇<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/999.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"21ffde4d2e6194508d37857f988bea66802cd6ac","tid":874455,"uid":122,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-10-24T08:14:28.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://i.gifer.com/3EVQ.gif\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fi.gifer.com%2F3EVQ.gif&h=73c6d199&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"d020e2a810d9732d2854e784f87cfab7eb04a21c","tid":874455,"uid":107297,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-10-24T08:14:35.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"7614d7f71cb3ef336ea031a3708f3a1f7287a978","tid":874455,"uid":158145,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-10-24T08:16:02.000Z","msg":"咁叻就唔洗打劫啦"},{"pid":"af8c635117f188ce37ecafa314e76ff827093773","tid":874455,"uid":5649,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-10-24T08:17:47.000Z","msg":"6條友搶士多<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n35成群咩"},{"pid":"7e32a57c10586dcb5c915ec6da862f12224c8df1","tid":874455,"uid":20658,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"af8c635117f188ce37ecafa314e76ff827093773","tid":874455,"uid":5649,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-10-24T08:17:47.000Z","msg":"6條友搶士多<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n35成群咩"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-10-24T08:47:12.000Z","msg":"士多？"}]}